get this place back on its feet.

454
00:19:43,816 --> 00:19:46,256
And I don't want you to
jeopardize that because of me.

455
00:19:52,941 --> 00:19:54,519
What did our legal team say?

456
00:19:54,543 --> 00:19:56,310
Um, yeah, they
said that we should

457
00:19:56,379 --> 00:19:58,112
settle now, quickly and quietly.

458
00:19:58,181 --> 00:20:00,108
What if we don't? ALEX:
If this thing goes to trial

459
00:20:00,132 --> 00:20:01,843
and there's a judgment
against us, we could owe millions

460
00:20:01,867 --> 00:20:03,511
or we could settle
this for much less.

461
00:20:03,535 --> 00:20:05,847
