bankruptcy all over again.

462
00:20:05,871 --> 00:20:08,088
Only if we lose. There's
another side to this.

463
00:20:08,157 --> 00:20:10,435
If Callie isn't settling,
maybe neither should we.

464
00:20:10,459 --> 00:20:12,209
Uh, no. I was there.

465
00:20:12,278 --> 00:20:13,822
I saw firsthand what
happened with this patient.

466
00:20:13,846 --> 00:20:16,797
And he has a case. A
good case. We should settle.

467
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:19,411
And, frankly,
Callie should, too.

468
00:20:19,435 --> 00:20:21,379
Dr. Yang, what is your
