473
00:20:30,946 --> 00:20:32,290
Is that right? That's right.

474
00:20:32,314 --> 00:20:34,214
Why was that?

475
00:20:34,283 --> 00:20:36,161
Because she was the best
orthopedic surgeon I knew.

476
00:20:36,185 --> 00:20:40,921
Was? As in past tense?

477
00:20:40,990 --> 00:20:43,230
You don't believe
she's the best anymore?

478
00:20:44,477 --> 00:20:46,517
There are vegetations
all over his aortic valve.

479
00:20:46,546 --> 00:20:47,873
Why didn't you page me sooner?

480
00:20:47,897 --> 00:20:48,973
We just heard the
murmur this morning.

481
00:20:48,997 --> 00:20:50,859
This morning? Yeah.

