infection is eating away at his graft.

486
00:20:58,574 --> 00:21:00,919
Best case, I go in,
clean it out and repair it.

487
00:21:00,943 --> 00:21:02,893
Worst case, he needs
a whole new valve.

488
00:21:02,962 --> 00:21:06,597
Dr. Torres, you
need to see this.

489
00:21:06,666 --> 00:21:08,811
I was changing his
compression socks and I saw this.

490
00:21:08,835 --> 00:21:10,967
His leg's gray, cold.
