00:33:10,939 --> 00:33:12,783
Travis would've
lost his leg for sure.

773
00:33:12,807 --> 00:33:15,503
I was just picking which
disaster to tackle first.

774
00:33:15,527 --> 00:33:17,738
<i>I cannot believe you're
picking this fight right now!</i>

