792
00:34:10,715 --> 00:34:12,076
<i>Tell her to get out!</i>
WHITNEY: <i>Travis...</i>

793
00:34:12,100 --> 00:34:14,601
I don't want her here.
Kick her out, Whit, now!

794
00:34:14,670 --> 00:34:16,787
God knows I can't
do it by myself.

795
00:34:16,855 --> 00:34:19,756
So get her the hell out of here!

796
00:34:19,824 --> 00:34:22,108
What's wrong with you?
Why aren't you doing anything?

797
00:34:22,177 --> 00:34:24,711
Okay, that's enough!

798
00:34:24,779 --> 00:34:27,997
Whitney, go to the family
lounge and get a snack.

799
00:34:28,067 --> 00:34:29,499
We need a minute, okay?

800
00:34:43,398 --> 00:34:45,949
Don't you dare
take this out on her.

