00:37:57,992 --> 00:37:59,903
and that could end your career.

864
00:37:59,927 --> 00:38:01,038
Not because you were negligent

865
00:38:01,062 --> 00:38:02,690
and not because you
did anything wrong.

866
00:38:02,714 --> 00:38:05,181
But because you feel bad?
Because you feel guilty?

867
00:38:05,249 --> 00:38:07,967
Let's not confuse
emotion with fact.

868
00:38:08,036 --> 00:38:11,888
And the fact is, you
did nothing wrong.

869
00:38:11,956 --> 00:38:13,656
Yes, I did.

870
00:38:16,695 --> 00:38:17,960
Hey.

871
00:38:19,263 --> 00:38:21,147
Okay. Thanks.

872
00:38:22,617 --> 00:38:24,683
They've reached a verdict.

873
00:38:27,188 --> 00:38:29,923
<i>We've all done things
we aren't proud of.</i>

874
00:38:34,229 --> 00:38:35,929
<i>I understand that.</i>

875
00:38:38,633 --> 00:38:40,649
<i>I know nobody's perfect.</i>

876
00:38:43,271 --> 00:38:45,288
<i>But how do you live with it?</i>

877
00:38:48,059 --> 00:38:50,438
<i>How do you get up every
morning and face the world,</i>

878
00:38:50,462 --> 00:38:53,312
<i>knowing you
could've done better?</i>

879
00:38:53,381 --> 00:38:55,221
<i>That you should've done better?</i>

880
00:38:59,504 --> 00:39:01,404
<i>Is being sorry enough?</i>

881
00:39:06,394 --> 00:39:09,111
<i>Can an apology
