00:39:17,388 --> 00:39:18,855
<i>Ease our pain?</i>

883
00:39:40,879 --> 00:39:43,329
<i>Can it undo the hurt
that we've caused?</i>

884
00:39:53,775 --> 00:39:55,352
<i>I really don't think so, Dad.</i>

885
00:39:55,376 --> 00:39:59,945
It's not enough. Just
because she says she's sorry...

886
00:40:00,014 --> 00:40:04,049
You're married. You took a vow.
