were stronger than one mistake.

898
00:40:34,299 --> 00:40:37,217
And I thank God
every day she did.

899
00:40:37,285 --> 00:40:40,052
Because otherwise,
I wouldn't have you.

900
00:40:42,591 --> 00:40:45,358
Thirty-eight years.
We've shared a life.

901
00:40:46,645 --> 00:40:49,579
And it all started
after that one mistake.

